Package veslo.client.converter

Class ExtensionConverterFactory

java.lang.Object
retrofit2.Converter.Factory
veslo.client.converter.ExtensionConverterFactory
Direct Known Subclasses:
GsonConverterFactory, JacksonConverterFactory
public class ExtensionConverterFactory
extends retrofit2.Converter.Factory
Universal converter factory. Allows you to match models and converters by: - annotation Converters, RequestConverter, ResponseConverter - package - class - Content-Type header value (MIME) - Java type (reference/primitive)

Author:
Oleg Shaburov (shaburov.o.a@gmail.com) Created: 20.11.2021

    • getExtensionConverter

      @Nullable protected ExtensionConverter<?> getExtensionConverter​(@Nonnull Annotation annotation, @Nonnull Type bodyType)
      Retrieves ExtensionConverter from ResponseConverter or RequestConverter annotations (Hereinafter, A). If method A.bodyClasses() returned an empty array, new instance of 'A.converter()' will be returned. If method A.bodyClasses() returned a non-empty list, a comparison by bodyClass will be performed, and if there is a match, new instance of A.converter() will be returned otherwise null.
      Parameters:
      annotation - - ResponseConverter or RequestConverter annotation
      bodyType - - model class
      Returns:
      ExtensionConverter or null
      Throws:
      ConvertCallException - if annotation differs from ResponseConverter or RequestConverter
